  ### `globalImportRemoteImage`

  **Type:** `boolean`

  **Default:** `false`

  Whether the [`importRemoteImage`](/en/api/importRemoteImage) API be available globally or not. If `true`, it can be used in any components or scripts without importing it.

  > **Note:** When `true`, a TS file named `import-remote-image.d.ts` containing the type for the `importRemoteImage` API will be created in the root directory of the project. If an `auto-import.d.ts` file exists, the type will be appended to it instead.
</Markdown>

